column1: 971 Americans died yesterday due to COVID-19. Republicans are not pro-life they are COVID deniers. #COVID19 https://t.co/YTxT09m9DG

The fastest and most effective way to help the families in Illinois harmed by economic impacts of COVID-19 is with direct cash payments. My colleagues and I are pushing for legislation that would establish payments of $2000 a month for adults and $1000 for children.

It is clear that this one-time stimulus is not enough to meet Americans’ needs. We must establish monthly payments and we must increase the amount of money received to help people like Magdalena and Arica make ends meet for the length of the COVID-19 crisis.
Since the beginning of the coronavirus crisis nearly one million Illinois residents have filed for unemployment benefits — more than one of every 10 Illinois workers.
From a plan to a bill I’m proud to be partnering with @ewarren on this critical legislation to ensure we have what we need to fight COVID-19 & protect Americans. #GetUsPPE https://t.co/y5oU8VT7iV
